Summary: two circles 1 big 1 small stuck together
trends: There have been 12 other sightings in Dublin

divs: Sighting Detailshi. i was walking my dog and as i arrived back into my housing estate, at the back of the houses facing me there was a circle about 10ft in diameter with a smaller circle about the size of a football stuck to the back of it,the larger circle was coloured green and white(like green and white paint were mixing together)and the smaller circle was a brillant white.there was no noise and it was at a height of about 50-70ft,the circles continued along the back of the houses until it got to my house then turned a sharp 35-45degrees towards the open fields at the back off the houses(also the direction of dublin airport) by this time i was in my back garden having watched it as i ran towards my house.seeing this i felt excited at no time did i feel in any harm thank you.
